IMU with STM32F1
================

Description: Convert MPU6050 raw gyro and accelerometer values to pitch and
yaw degrees. Complementary filter was used to smoothen the calibrated output.

To install and run on local machine, clone this repo, and set up PlatformIO
accordingly to the STM32F1 Blue Pill board.

This branch use the `STM32duino` framework. For one that uses the standardized
HAL, check out the `hal` branch.
